{"tid":2144711,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"唔想香港變新彊嘅就唔好去參加咩全民檢測方案","createTime":"2020-08-07T17:20:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-07T17:51:21.000Z","uid":344792,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"7686636439d7e791b0e5890ad2066d9880f184a0","tid":2144711,"uid":344792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T17:20:54.000Z","msg":"今日林鄭開咗記招講<span class=\"purple\">全民檢測方案</span><br />\n當中就會派三間中国級劍測化驗所負責做社區檢測<br />\n包括<span class=\"red\"> 華大</span>、金域、凱普<br />\n而<span class=\"red\">華大已經係中山紀念公園起實驗室</span><br />\n<span class=\"red\">華大</span>係被美國商務部列入黑名單入面<br />\n佢被指控涉嫌<span class=\"blue\">強制採集維族人基因研究</span><br />\n衛生局曾經以「急切需要短時間內展開大規模檢測」為由去聘用<span class=\"red\">華昇診斷中心</span><br />\n都係<span class=\"red\">華大</span>企下嘅<br />\n睇到呢到相信大家都知發生咩事<br />\n唔想香港變成新彊嘅 唔想dna被送中嘅<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">記住記住唔好去驗</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gYbgtVV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgYbgtVV.png&h=9f0932c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B2Vdv9H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB2Vdv9H.jpg&h=22ba9fb8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bb683d6dd0b7d35dfe205468f7570b19fe8b27cf","tid":2144711,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T17:21:18.000Z","msg":"除咗制裁，今日係梓樂離開9個月<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2144688\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2144688</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ccyVKr4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FccyVKr4.png&h=fbc64625&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5tWka9x.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5tWka9x.png&h=850fb110&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8075a6cc00e5df2349d18509a9b0cd2bff5cdae8","tid":2144711,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T17:22:00.000Z","msg":"【多圖】政府要你飲